fields.title: Jewelry Store | TUR
fields.description: A contemporary jewelry boutique designed with a modern luxury approach. The space combines elegant minimalism with high-end finishes such as marble, glass, and brass details to highlight the brilliance of the collections. Clean lines, curated lighting, and custom display units create a refined atmosphere where each piece of jewelry becomes the true centerpiece. The design emphasizes exclusivity, sophistication, and a seamless customer journey — from the entrance to private consultation areas.

fields.title: 15-20 minutes neighbourhood
fields.description: CONCEPT: The 20-minute neighbourhood concept is an urban design and planning strategy aimed at creating communities where residents can meet most of their daily needs within a 20-minute walk, cycle, or public transport trip from their homes. This approach focuses on enhancing liveability, sustainability, and accessibility, fostering a higher quality of life by reducing dependency on cars and promoting healthier Lifestyle.

fields.title: Luxurious Modern Master Bedroom Design
fields.description: This luxurious modern bedroom, located in KSA, is designed to offer both comfort and elegance within a total area of 21.5m². The room features sleek, minimalist furnishings combined with high-end finishes to create a serene and opulent atmosphere. Large windows invite natural light, while carefully placed ambient lighting enhances the room's spaciousness. Plush materials and contemporary decor elements complete the design, making this bedroom a perfect retreat for relaxation and sophistication.

fields.title: Cafe Design | KSA
fields.description: A modern café counter with a sleek white and brown color scheme. The menu is displayed on four red hanging boards with white text. The counter includes a built-in illuminated display showcasing fresh pastries and desserts. Black barstools line the front of the counter, which is covered in textured brown tiles. Pendant lights hang from the ceiling, adding a warm ambiance. The background features a brick accent wall with a row of coffee bags on display, along with framed black-and-white photographs of musical instruments and microphones, enhancing the café’s artistic and cozy atmosphere.

fields.title: Furniture Design for Matte Shop
fields.description: A custom furniture collection designed specifically for a modern matte-finish retail shop. The pieces feature sleek lines, minimal detailing, and a premium tactile experience. Dark matte woods, powder-coated metals, and soft-textured finishes create a refined and contemporary aesthetic. Each unit—display shelving, counters, and seating—has been designed for both function and visual impact, ensuring the shop interior reflects sophistication and brand identity.

fields.title: Villa Islamic Design - Execution Drawings
fields.description: Project: Villa 5+3 Location: London Project Area: 720 m² Ceiling Height: 3.10m Date: 06/2023

fields.title: Modern Hotel Facade Design & Execution Drawings
fields.description: by Alexandria Designs | Led by Muhammad Ali Aboelhamd Project Scope: This project focuses on the complete facade design and execution drawings for a modern hotel located in a vibrant urban context. The design blends contemporary aesthetics, functional detailing, and local identity, with an emphasis on clean geometry, dynamic material interplay, and climate-responsive elements. Tools Used: Revit | AutoCAD | 3Ds Max | V-Ray | Photoshop | BIM 360 Key Features: Sun shading systems and energy-efficient glazing Rhythmic pattern in façade composition Integration of lighting strategy with architectural elements Executed in line with hotel brand identity and hospitality codes.

fields.title: Exhibition Entrance Design | Watch & Jewellery Middle East Show
fields.description: "Living Luxury" is a visionary collection of immersive spatial installations developed for the Watch & Jewellery Middle East Show. Each concept brings luxury to life through motion, light, and poetic form. These designs transcend traditional exhibition environments, crafting emotional, dynamic, and sensorial experiences. Concept Overviews: 1. Ethereal Motion A flowing installation of suspended fabric waves simulating the gentle rhythm of breath. It creates a dreamy atmosphere of lightness and movement, echoing the diamond’s shimmer and the elegance of air. 2. Living Facets An iconic entrance arch inspired by the multifaceted geometry of a diamond. Reflective surfaces and angular forms symbolize elegance in motion—luxury that breathes and refracts light with every step. 3. Breathing Luxury – Dynamic Columns Elegant sculptural columns expand and contract like lungs, breathing rhythmically as visitors pass through. This concept captures the motion of luxury—constantly alive, changing, and glowing. 4. Chasing Time An artistic expression of time’s elusive nature, inspired by the flight of a dragonfly. Organic forms, flowing textures, and light interplay embody the fleeting, poetic beauty of movement. 5. Bamboo Kinesis Inspired by the segmented flexibility of bamboo, this installation fuses biophilic design with luxurious materials. It symbolizes strength, sustainability, and elegant natural motion. 6. The Living Jewel A sculptural centerpiece of the event. A man and woman become one ethereal orchid—crafted from air, light, and fabric—symbolizing unity, beauty, and the essence of fine jewelry. Breathing, glowing, and evolving, it embodies jewelry’s relationship to the body and the soul.

fields.title: Shop Drawings – Matte Shop
fields.description: Preparation of detailed shop drawings for all custom-made furniture and interior elements within the Matte Shop. These drawings will ensure accurate fabrication, coordination, and installation on-site.

fields.title: Office Building | Interior Design | Execution Drawing
fields.description: A contemporary executive office design featuring refined neutral tones, bespoke furniture, and integrated ambient lighting. The layout combines functionality with sophistication, offering executive desks, a modern conference area, and curated wall art to create a professional and elegant workspace.

fields.title: HOUSING IN NEW COMMUNITIES
fields.description: ALAMEIN NEW CITY–NORTHWEST COAST Nature is the symbol of life, giving and comfort, so we need nature to be closer to us to renew the daily activity of man. By Providing comfortable and contemporary living needs with livable open spaces, good environmental conditions and a batter social life. A surface used from the sides in closed rooms with curtains walls, used as a gym, leisure and activity halls, cafes, etc. And in the center it is used for parties and sitting with enjoying the view around it under pergolas. The hierarchical shape in the gradient provides places to sit with complete privacy and gradually integrate with nature.

fields.title: Bedroom Design | | Execution Drawings
fields.description: A luxurious modern bedroom featuring a statement upholstered headboard wall, soft neutral tones, and refined material combinations including marble, metal, and dark mirrors. Elegant bedside tables, layered textures, and a contemporary chandelier enhance the sense of comfort and sophistication.

fields.title: VIP Seating Area
fields.description: A futuristic VIP seating area designed for gamers, featuring curved sofas, neon LED lighting, mirrored surfaces, and digital screens. The space combines metal, concrete, and vibrant colors to create an immersive, high-tech gaming atmosphere.

fields.title: Kitchen Execution Drawings
fields.description: The Main Kitchen is designed with a refined modern aesthetic, combining clean lines with warm natural finishes. High-quality cabinetry, elegant stone surfaces, and integrated lighting create a sophisticated yet functional environment. This space is tailored for both style and efficiency, offering a contemporary kitchen experience that blends comfort with timeless design.

fields.title: Coffee Shop Execution Drawings
fields.description: This café interior blends creativity and comfort through a vibrant palette of teal and pink, paired with bold graphic patterns and artistic wall illustrations. Designed to be both inviting and visually striking, the space offers a unique and memorable atmosphere that enhances the customer experience and reflects a modern, playful brand identity.

fields.title: Digital Creativity House - Small Firm HeadQuarter Alamein New City
fields.description: Concept: Building Types develop and change overtime in addition to innovative prototypes for we are forced to make the buildings highly customizable, changeable and concerning human needs and relationships to maximize the outcome Aim: The building is divided into two parts: one is stable for services & the other is customizable for rooms and office area by using steel structure, partition walls and transformable Furniture. Make the building sustainable to help the environment & to improve the human health. Environmental Technology: Solar panel photovoltaic panels with light weight, freely designable & easy to install Green roof system with thin layer , can be easily installed in existing buildings & light weight.
